A Florida woman is facing life in prison after she was convicted of killing her estranged husband during a 'date rape' sex game.

Anita Smithey, 46, sobbed and collapsed in court after she was found guilty of second degree murder following the death of Robert Cline III in May 2010.

She shot him in his Oviedo, Florida, home while they were having sex during violent role play which involved using a knife as a prop. 

